45
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:18,560
Here.

46
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,200
Take this.

47
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,280
Guo Zijie!

48
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,120
Go now.

49
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,280
Sun Weiyan!

50
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,480
Guo Zijie!

51
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:28,880
Sun Weiyan!

52
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:29,640
Xuanxuan.

53
00:03:30,660 --> 00:03:31,560
What's the matter?

54
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:32,680
Where's Zijie?

55
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,240
