were searching for Li Ye.

56
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,520
But don't worry.

57
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,040
Li Ye is a weak scholar.

58
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,440
He Chun is a skilled martial artist.

59
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:40,600
It's easy to catch him.

60
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,500
I don't think this matter
is that simple.

61
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:43,560
You're right.

62
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,720
Li Ye has been to this mountain.

63
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:46,920
If he wants to hide,

64
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,780
He Chun will need to put in some effort.

65
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,880
Think about it.

66
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,960
Li Ye was always present

67
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,480
when we were investigating the case.

68
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,960
But we never suspected him.

69
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,200
Why did he run?

70
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,240
I think

71
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,120
this might be

72
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:00,640
because Li Ye...

73
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:03,640
You...

74
00:04:06,480 --> 00:04:08,120
It was she
who disrespected Fox Spirit.

75
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,440
She's trying to get us all killed!

76
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,120
There's no such thing as Fox Spirit.

77
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,120
Fox Spirit doesn't exist.

78
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,200
Yes, there's no Fox Spirit.

79
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:13,880
It's you!

80
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,260
You're trying to get us all killed!

81
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:15,700
It's you!

82
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:16,300
She's the one.

83
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:17,420
We must not let her go!

84
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:18,000
What?

85
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,920
Listen to me!

86
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,920
Don't let her go!

87
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,320
- Let me explain.
- We can talk.

88
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:21,760
It was her.

89
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,700
- She wants us killed! Catch her!
- Listen to me!

90
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:24,600
Don't let her go!

91
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,360
Catch her!

92
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,160
Everyone! Calm down!

93
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,680
Catch her!

94
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,640
She's trying to kill us!

95
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,200
Listen to me!

96
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:28,940
We won't spare you.

97
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:30,220
We can't let her leave!

98
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,120
Get her!

99
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:31,920
Don't let her go!

100
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:33,040
Don't run!

101
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,800
Don't let her escape!

102
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:36,000
Get her!

103
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:36,920
It's you!

104
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:39,040
She's the one
who tried to get us killed.

105
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,600
It was her!

106
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:40,040
Get her!

107
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,080
Help!

108
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,280
Get her!

109
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,680
Let me go!

110
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,720
Don't let her get away!

111
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,600
Keep this a secret.

112
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:01,940
Let's get out of here.

113
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:02,500
Come on.

114
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:03,380
Let's go.

115
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,240
It's done.

116
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,800
Don't let this matter get out.

117
00:05:10,940 --> 00:05:11,480
Understood.

118
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,340
You can go now.

119
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:17,880
Sun Weiyan!

120
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:19,760
Zijie!

121
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,800
Have you found them?

122
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,520
He Chun went to find Li Ye.

123
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:25,840
What about Xuanxuan?

124
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,080
Xuanxuan?

125
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:28,640
I thought you suspected her.

126
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,160
So I took the chance

127
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,400
to help you

128
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:32,300
get rid of her.

129
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,320
What did you do?

130
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:37,080
I found several villagers

131
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,160
to push her off the cliff.

132
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:43,560
Zijie!

133
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,020
Better to wrong a thousand

134
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,000
than let one escape!

135
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,860
You're ridiculous!

136
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:49,720
How stubborn.

137
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,840
Help!

138
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:56,000
Help!

139
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,760
Help!

140
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,920
Help!

141
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,320
Xuanxuan, don't be scared!

142
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,400
I'm coming to save you!

143
00:06:19,340 --> 00:06:22,140
♪I think I'm exceptionally affectionate♪

144
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:25,180
♪Devotion can warm the coldest ice♪

145
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:28,940
♪And you're a shooting star
that flashes by♪

146
00:06:29,460 --> 00:06:32,500
♪Out of reach♪

147
00:06:32,820 --> 00:06:36,020
♪I prayed for a miracle countless times♪

148
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:40,260
♪If I meet you, I only wish
we could be together forever♪

149
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:46,060
♪But only the distant phantom remains♪

150
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:49,700
♪Love rises like the wind
but remains unsettled when it stops♪

151
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:53,180
♪Chasing you through four seasons,
wandering for a lifetime♪

152
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:55,060
♪Fish in the water is greedy♪

153
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:59,940
♪For the reflection
of clouds in the heart of the lake♪

154
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:03,700
♪From dusk to dawn,
from heavy snow to early clear sky♪

155
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:08,140
♪Searching for your footprints
from south to west♪

156
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:14,700
♪The wind stops,
but the dream isn't over♪

157
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:19,580
♪But the cloud is only a shadow
in the end♪

158
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:23,880
I didn't expect

159
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,240
you to be quite heavy.

160
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,040
I'm not heavy.

161
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,280
You're the one who's heavy.

162
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:31,760
Are you all right?

163
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,560
I'm fine.

164
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:35,760
About

165
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:37,160
just now,

166
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,520
thank you.

167
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,280
It's nothing.

168
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,360
It's something I should do.

169
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:49,280
Those rural villagers went too far.

170
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,840
I will punish them properly

171
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:52,000
after I get back.

172
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:19,040
Let's go.

173
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:27,600
Xuanxuan.

174
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,480
Let me go.

175
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:29,520
Let me explain.

176
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,520
Explain?

177
00:08:32,060 --> 00:08:34,180
Are you going to say
it's related to your brother?

178
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,760
I admit your behaviors were different

179
00:08:35,780 --> 00:08:37,440
after you woke up.

180
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,600
I did suspect you were sent by Brother.

181
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:40,600
So...

182
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:41,920
So...

183
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,080
So

184
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,880
you put all these baseless charges

185
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,720
on an innocent person

186
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,240
and have her killed, is that it?

187
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,000
Guo Zijie,

188
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,080
your foolishness is an act,

189
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:53,640
your kindness is an act,

190
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,360
and everything about you is an act!

191
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:58,280
You've never trusted me, have you?

192
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,640
Fine.

193
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:01,200
I don't ever want to see you again.

194
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:02,840
Let me go!

195
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:03,720
Xuanxuan,

196
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:04,600
listen to me.

197
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:05,880
Yes, I admit.

198
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,320
I hesitated.

199
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,560
It was my fault.

200
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,560
I didn't trust you enough back then.

201
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,480
But I came around after a while.

202
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:14,520
I don't care if Brother sent you

203
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:17,120
or if you were Cao Xuanxuan from before.

204
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,000
I could never do something like that

205
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,320
because you were the one

206
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:23,000
who showed up and stayed by my side

207
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:25,320
when I was at my lowest.

208
00:09:37,780 --> 00:09:38,320
Xuanxuan!

209
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:38,900
Magistrate Guo!

210
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:39,360
Xuanxuan.

211
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:40,200
Magistrate Guo.

212
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:41,900
Something bad has happened!

213
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,480
Master Luo Ji's body is missing.

214
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,080
Sir,

215
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,660
you need to go and check right away!

216
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:48,840
Sir.

217
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,880
What happened?

218
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,240
Check on Xuanxuan for me.

219
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:52,640
All right.

220
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,160
Sir.

221
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:56,480
Sir.

222
00:09:59,160 --> 00:09:59,880
Let's go.

223
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,840
Young Master Zilu.

224
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:12,840
Where do you think you can run to?

225
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:15,960
What is it?

226
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:17,960
Liu Ying failed.

227
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,760
Useless thing.

228
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:29,840
I thought she might still be
of some use.

229
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:33,780
The people involved
in the Lyu Residence case

230
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:35,040
are all important figures.

231
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:37,180
One of the victims
is the Imperial Envoy.

232
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,440
If Guo Zijie solves this case,

233
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,580
he will be praised
by His Majesty.

234
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:42,940
Young Master Zilu,

235
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:44,320
stop hesitating.

236
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,320
Guo Zijie, that fool.

237
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:51,240
I thought I would just get rid
of Cao Xuanxuan

238
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:54,960
to spare him since we are brothers.

239
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,360
But who would have thought...

240
00:10:57,560 --> 00:10:59,160
Things have already come to this point,

241
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,720
and there's no turning back.

242
00:11:01,420 --> 00:11:02,620
Young Master Zilu,

243
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,100
everything is ready.

244
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,720
We only need your command.

245
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:17,560
Go.

246
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:18,920
Rest assured.

247
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:19,880
This time,

248
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,760
it'll be done fast without a trace.

249
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,440
Guo Zijie,

250
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,040
you jerk.

251
00:12:06,900 --> 00:12:07,880
Who's there?

252
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:16,640
Xuanxuan!

253
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:18,560
Xuanxuan!

254
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,600
Xuanxuan!

255
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:44,600
Sir!

256
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:46,840
Bad news.

257
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,200
Xuanxuan is in danger.

258
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:00,840
This way.

259
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:07,600
Right here.

260
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:23,900
Let's split up and search.

261
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:25,100
- All right.
- All right.

262
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:43,440
Xuanxuan!

263
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:45,640
Xuanxuan!

264
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,800
(Xuanxuan,)

265
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:05,840
(wait for me.)

266
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,440
(I'll save you.)

267
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:20,240
Xuanxuan!

268
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:21,600
Xuanxuan!

269
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:27,520
Xuanxuan!

270
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:35,880
You're finally here.

271
00:14:39,560 --> 00:14:40,000
Xuanxuan!

272
00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:47,840
I'm the one you want.

273
00:14:48,280 --> 00:14:48,800
Let her go.

274
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:52,760
You're pretty clever.

275
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:55,580
No wonder someone wants to kill you.

276
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,480
Since you're aware of the situation,

277
00:14:57,760 --> 00:14:59,400
we don't want to escalate things either.

278
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,240
If you drink this,

279
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,360
we'll let her go right away.

280
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:12,480
It's Bloodfang Toxin again.

281
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:13,640
Stop wasting time

282
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:14,920
before we kill her.

283
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:19,560
Fine.

284
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:20,920
I'll drink it.

285
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:33,800
Tell the one who ordered you

286
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:36,760
to take care of my father.

287
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:48,440
