583
00:28:52,760 --> 00:28:53,880
No one would believe

584
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,240
a dead person can kill.

585
00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:57,360
But Mr. Zhao didn't expect

586
00:28:57,360 --> 00:28:59,920
Luo Ji intended to kill him.

587
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:01,740
You can get back to work.

588
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,080
I don't get it.

589
00:29:15,880 --> 00:29:16,880
Even if

590
00:29:17,160 --> 00:29:19,280
Luo managed to gain Mr. Zhao's trust,

591
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:21,120
the door lock was not damaged.

592
00:29:21,600 --> 00:29:22,760
How did he get in?

593
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:23,880
He has a point.

594
00:29:24,080 --> 00:29:24,780
That's right.

595
00:29:24,820 --> 00:29:25,760
How did he enter?

596
00:29:26,141 --> 00:29:27,280
Can't make sense of this.

597
00:29:27,280 --> 00:29:28,320
Could it be...

598
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:30,520
Lyu,

599
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:32,240
is it you?

600
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:33,480
Ridiculous!

601
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:35,160
Don't speak nonsense

602
00:29:35,320 --> 00:29:36,400
at a time like this.

603
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,840
How could it be me?

604
00:29:38,729 --> 00:29:39,240
He's right.

605
00:29:39,520 --> 00:29:40,760
Lyu, look at this letter.

606
00:29:40,760 --> 00:29:41,380
(Dear Xiuniang)

607
00:29:42,040 --> 00:29:43,000
I got this letter

608
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,560
from Second Madam.

609
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:46,560
Second Madam has lived alone
for many years

610
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:48,120
and had long been involved with Luo Ji.

611
00:29:48,720 --> 00:29:49,800
Luo Ji used Second Madam

612
00:29:49,800 --> 00:29:51,400
to change the unbreakable lock
in secret.

613
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:53,120
(Everything is going well.)
When Second Madam

614
00:29:53,120 --> 00:29:54,600
(I'm achieving everything.)
heard Luo Ji died,

615
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:55,660
she wanted to seek revenge.

616
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:57,840
She just happened
to witness Luo Ji killing Mr. Zhao

617
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,840
and thought she had seen a ghost.

618
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:00,960
That's why

619
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:02,680
she ended up in such a state.

620
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:04,960
So that was what happened.

621
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:05,840
I see.

622
00:30:06,160 --> 00:30:07,160
That was unexpected.

623
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,520
So that was how it went.

624
00:30:09,520 --> 00:30:10,960
We were friends.

625
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:12,800
Why would Luo want

626
00:30:13,040 --> 00:30:14,440
to kill Mr. Zhao?

627
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:17,080
I understand now.

628
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:19,520
It must be because of that incident.

629
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:22,560
Mr. Zhao was assigned a case back then,

630
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:24,960
which led to Luo Ji losing his parents.

631
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:28,280
But later, the case was overturned
and corrected.

632
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:30,320
Mr. Zhao never wanted

633
00:30:30,320 --> 00:30:31,520
Luo Ji to know

634
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:33,080
he handled that case.

635
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:35,000
But now it seems

636
00:30:36,040 --> 00:30:37,840
Luo Ji found out.

637
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:41,040
But how did Luo fake his death?

638
00:30:41,220 --> 00:30:42,480
We clearly saw his dead body

639
00:30:42,480 --> 00:30:43,840
in front of us that day.

640
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:46,200
Guo Zijie,

641
00:30:47,940 --> 00:30:49,440
carry the candle stand here.

642
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:52,680
Now.

643
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:55,400
The one at the entrance.

644
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:19,600
Make way.

645
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:26,360
This is the candle stand.

646
00:31:30,320 --> 00:31:30,880
So it's...

647
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:32,800
It turns out...

648
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:35,120
It turns out to be a flat surface.

649
00:31:37,720 --> 00:31:38,720
Incredible!

650
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:39,660
I didn't expect this.

651
00:31:39,700 --> 00:31:41,480
Mrs. Guo is really something.

652
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,680
Good thing Mrs. Guo discovered this.

653
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:44,680
Magistrate Guo,

654
00:31:44,840 --> 00:31:46,280
you've found yourself a great wife!

655
00:31:46,280 --> 00:31:46,800
That's right.

656
00:31:46,800 --> 00:31:48,200
She's really intelligent.

657
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,040
Ah, yes.

658
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:53,480
That explains everything, then.

659
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:54,200
Luo Ji.

660
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:55,320
This darn Luo Ji.

661
00:31:55,320 --> 00:31:56,320
Where is he now?

662
00:31:56,760 --> 00:31:58,960
Since the truth of this case
is now clear,

663
00:31:59,180 --> 00:32:01,160
I'll issue an arrest warrant
throughout the city

664
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,220
to have him captured.

665
00:32:02,280 --> 00:32:03,420
He won't be able to escape.

666
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:04,480
That's great.

667
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:06,180
- He won't escape.
- That's right.

668
00:32:06,180 --> 00:32:07,280
When did you figure it out?

669
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:07,960
I'm hungry.

670
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:09,040
Let's eat something.

671
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:12,790
She's...

672
00:32:12,913 --> 00:32:13,240
Why...

673
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:14,440
What's wrong with her?

674
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:17,720
Zijie,

675
00:32:18,080 --> 00:32:19,520
we really shouldn't offend women.

676
00:32:29,460 --> 00:32:32,740
(The task is complete.
Please provide the next move.)

677
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:38,600
You've been working hard

678
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:39,800
over the past few days.

679
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:42,280
You're welcome.

680
00:32:42,760 --> 00:32:43,680
Actually,

681
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:46,120
we have a request.

682
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:47,320
Mrs. Guo,

683
00:32:47,320 --> 00:32:48,380
please tell me what it is.

684
00:32:49,280 --> 00:32:49,960
Well...

685
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:50,840
Well,

686
00:32:50,840 --> 00:32:53,840
we heard that a Western artist
visited your residence.

687
00:32:53,880 --> 00:32:55,000
We would like to meet him.

688
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,280
That Western artist?

689
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:59,240
He prefers peace and quiet.

690
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,780
So I let him stay at a different place.

691
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:01,440
How about this?

692
00:33:01,600 --> 00:33:03,200
I'll send someone to invite him over.

693
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:03,880
Everyone,

694
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:04,760
please take a seat

695
00:33:04,760 --> 00:33:05,560
and have some rest.

696
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:06,760
I'll be right back.

697
00:33:07,120 --> 00:33:07,680
Thank you.

698
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:08,640
Thank you.

699
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:09,000
Come.

700
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:09,720
Take a seat.

701
00:33:30,740 --> 00:33:31,440
Magistrate Guo!

702
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:31,960
He's here.

703
00:33:32,600 --> 00:33:33,080
I'm back.

704
00:33:35,080 --> 00:33:35,560
Hello.

705
00:33:35,560 --> 00:33:36,200
Here he is.

706
00:33:36,200 --> 00:33:37,800
So you're the Western artist?

707
00:33:38,040 --> 00:33:39,440
Yes, I am.

708
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:40,720
May I know

709
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:41,880
why you want to see me?

710
00:33:42,040 --> 00:33:43,120
Yes, we wanted to see you.

711
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:45,960
Please wait for a moment.

712
00:33:50,060 --> 00:33:51,280
I'll leave if it's nothing.

713
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,200
Wait.

714
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:53,440
We want you to verify something.

715
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:54,440
Please wait for a while.

716
00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:55,280
That's right.

717
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:56,360
This one.

718
00:33:56,680 --> 00:33:57,440
It's here.

719
00:33:58,280 --> 00:33:58,880
Well,

720
00:33:59,200 --> 00:33:59,920
may I know

721
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,400
if you've seen such a thing?

722
00:34:05,600 --> 00:34:06,520
I made it.

723
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:08,140
What is it that you'd like to say?

724
00:34:09,160 --> 00:34:10,160
Did you really make this?

725
00:34:10,160 --> 00:34:11,520
Who else could do this besides me?

726
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:13,160
Then can you tell me

727
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:14,800
what inspired you to build this?

728
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:16,880
Young lass,

729
00:34:17,240 --> 00:34:18,800
how many artists have you actually met?

730
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:20,200
How dare you doubt me?

731
00:34:20,300 --> 00:34:22,240
I'm not going to entertain
any of your questions.

732
00:34:22,300 --> 00:34:23,000
Mr. Lyu,

733
00:34:23,140 --> 00:34:24,700
is this why you asked me to come over?

734
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:25,720
I'm leaving.

735
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,440
Mister!

736
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:28,320
Mister!

737
00:34:41,720 --> 00:34:42,400
Master,

738
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:43,880
are you worried

739
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:45,800
about Young Master Zijie?

740
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,880
When I was young,

741
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:53,080
I looked forward to my birthday.

742
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:56,280
But as I get older,

743
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:58,160
I'm afraid of celebrating it.

744
00:35:00,480 --> 00:35:02,960
I'm worried
if Zijie can't make it this time,

745
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:04,320
he won't have another chance

746
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:06,240
to attend my birthday.

747
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:09,400
Master,

748
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:12,200
please don't say such things.

749
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:15,200
There's still next year.

750
00:35:16,240 --> 00:35:17,040
Next year?

751
00:35:21,080 --> 00:35:23,360
Next year, huh?

752
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:26,840
Next year...

753
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,640
(Zijie,)

754
00:35:47,640 --> 00:35:48,800
(forgive me.)

755
00:36:21,041 --> 00:36:26,921
♪Like the setting sun,
which repeatedly sets in the west♪

756
00:36:28,181 --> 00:36:33,621
♪My heart goes over mountains
to rest with you♪

757
00:36:34,781 --> 00:36:38,221
♪As the winds and clouds shift,
our encounter♪

758
00:36:38,221 --> 00:36:41,981
♪Seems like the perfect foreshadowing♪

759
00:36:42,381 --> 00:36:47,421
♪But it was a misplaced expectation♪

760
00:36:48,941 --> 00:36:52,021
♪I think I'm exceptionally affectionate♪

761
00:36:52,221 --> 00:36:55,141
♪Devotion can warm the coldest ice♪

762
00:36:55,501 --> 00:36:58,701
♪And you're a shooting star
that flashes by♪

763
00:36:59,141 --> 00:37:01,421
♪Out of reach♪

764
00:37:02,501 --> 00:37:05,701
♪I prayed for a miracle countless times♪

765
00:37:05,981 --> 00:37:10,101
♪If I meet you, I only wish
we could be together forever♪

766
00:37:10,381 --> 00:37:16,501
♪But only the distant phantom remains♪

767
00:37:16,621 --> 00:37:19,661
♪Love rises like the wind
but remains unsettled when it stops♪

768
00:37:19,941 --> 00:37:22,941
♪Chasing you through four seasons,
wandering for a lifetime♪

769
00:37:23,221 --> 00:37:24,901
♪Fish in the water♪

770
00:37:24,901 --> 00:37:30,141
♪Is greedy for the reflection
of clouds in the heart of the lake♪

771
00:37:30,341 --> 00:37:33,261
♪From dusk to dawn,
from heavy snow to early clear sky♪

772
00:37:33,461 --> 00:37:37,781
♪Searching for your footprints
from south to west♪

773
00:37:38,141 --> 00:37:43,781
♪The wind stops,
but the dream isn't over♪
